{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"ffeefc88-048a-423c-ba04-fe8851e5a6b0","content":"Your `.testsettings` has three settings to migrate. In MSTest v3, `.testsettings` is **no longer supported** — you need a `.runsettings` file instead.\n\nHere's the mapping:\n\n| `.testsettings` setting | `.runsettings` equivalent |\n|---|---|\n| `TestTimeout = 30000` | `<MSTest><TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout></MSTest>` |\n| Code Coverage DataCollector | `<DataCollectors>` section in `.runsettings` |\n| `useLoadContext=\"true\"` | No longer needed — MSTest v3 loads assemblies in context by default |\n\nLet me create the `.runsettings` file and update your project:","toolRequests":[{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_015vv6jzMFDvd2n6Xz8BT4zY","name":"report_intent","arguments":{"intent":"Creating runsettings migration"},"type":"function"},{"toolCallId":"toolu_vrtx_01VHKazG6xpMrvkczw9Z4sCG","name":"create","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/sv-f9085a8bf4574ce2937af5ff18bcb2bb/local.runsettings","file_text":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n<RunSettings>\n  <MSTest>\n    <TestTimeout>30000</TestTimeout>\n  </MSTest>\n  <DataCollectionRunSettings>\n    <DataCollectors>\n      <DataCollector friendlyName=\"Code Coverage\"\n        uri=\"datacollector://microsoft/CodeCoverage/2.0\"\n        assemblyQualifiedName=\"Microsoft.VisualStudio.TraceCollector.dll\">\n      </DataCollector>\n    </DataCollectors>\n  </DataCollectionRunSettings>\n</RunSettings>\n"},"type":"function","intentionSummary":"create a new file at /tmp/sv-f9085a8bf4574ce2937af5ff18bcb2bb/local.runsettings."}],"interactionId":"5b91ad8b-88da-4beb-9dd5-62c6457a5d2e","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The user has a `.testsettings` file with three key configurations:\n1. **Deployment/Assembly resolution** - `useLoadContext=\"true\"`\n2. **Test timeout** - 30000ms (30 seconds)\n3. **Code coverage data collector**\n\nIn MSTest v3, `.testsettings` files are no longer supported. The configuration needs to be migrated to a `.runsettings` file and/or MSTest v3 attributes/properties.\n\nLet me explain the migration path:\n\n1. **Test timeout**: In MSTest v3, you can set this via `[Timeout]` attribute per test, or via `.runsettings` with MSTest settings, or via `TestMethodOptions.DefaultTimeout` in `.runsettings`.\n\n\n2. **Code coverage**: This gets configured in `.runsettings` under the data collectors section.\n3. **Assembly resolution / deployment**: MSTest v3 handles this differently now—the `useLoadContext` setting isn't needed anymore since MSTest v3 uses a different test host model.\n\nI'll create a `.runsettings` file that handles these migrations.","outputTokens":730,"requestId":"241F:17B497:406E9D:4549C9:6A031075"},"id":"0d1822e4-5296-4d36-806f-f6080fe4f25c","timestamp":"2026-05-12T11:35:30.513Z","parentId":"8e9eefd3-42ca-4e10-b79b-01430782871d"}
